  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个餐厅桌位状态流转图。核心状态有四个：空闲（Livre）、已预订（Reservada）、占用中（Ocupada）和不可用（Indisponivel）。所有桌位最初从基础设施控制器进入空闲状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Livre",
        "Reservada",
        "Ocupada",
        "Indisponivel",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。空闲状态应该有两条主要出路对吧？一条是客人直接入座变成占用，另一条是被预订。那预订后客人到达时，应该流转到占用状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Livre",
        "Ocupada",
        "Reservada"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Reservada到Ocupada的触发条件是\"cliente chegou\"。另外占用结束后客人离开，桌位回到空闲。还有两种回到空闲的情况：预订被取消，或者从不可用状态恢复。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reservada",
        "Ocupada",
        "Livre",
        "Indisponivel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主流程画出来：Infra_IngressController指向Livre作为起点，然后Livre分出两条线——一条到Reservada标注\"reserva feita\"，一条到Ocupada标注\"cliente senta sem reserva\"。Reservada到Ocupada标注\"cliente chegou\"，Ocupada回到Livre标注\"cliente saiu\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Livre",
        "Reservada",
        "Ocupada"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还需要考虑桌位不可用的场景。维护时从空闲直接变成Indisponivel，紧急情况时占用中也可能需要强制下线，还有预订被系统锁定的情况。这三种都要能进入不可用状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Indisponivel",
        "Livre",
        "Ocupada",
        "Reservada"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：Livre到Indisponivel标注\"manutenção\"，Reservada到Indisponivel标注\"bloqueio\"，Ocupada到Indisponivel标注\"emergência\"。最后Indisponivel恢复后回到Livre，标注\"disponível novamente\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Indisponivel",
        "Livre",
        "Reservada",
        "Ocupada"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Reservada到Livre的流转我漏说了——预订取消时也要能回去。你刚才好像没画这条线？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reservada",
        "Livre"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "补上！Reservada到Livre添加标注\"reserva cancelada\"。现在所有状态流转都完整了，标题定为\"Diagrama de Estados - Status de Mesa\"，使用stateDiagram-v2语法。",
